1.1.name: wordpress/bp-xtra-signup
1.1.description: This plugin lets you add a Terms of Service checkbox and, optionally, a Mailchimp signup checkbox to your BuddyPress registration page. Additionally, an ajax username availability check, a password strength meter, email check and date of birth check can be activated.
